title: The network zoo
content:
The network zoo netZoo{R,Py,M,C} is a network biology package for the reconstruction and analysis of gene regulatory networks.
Packages R: netZooR
Python: netZooPy
MATLAB: netZooM
C: netZooC
netZoo{R,Py,M,C} is a community maintained package licensed under GPL-3.0.
